# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [Released]

### Added 
- Added AutoMapper for object.
- Added OrganizationMap.

### Changed
- CQRS Pattern validation.
- DatabaseContext increased protected level.
- AccountConsultion "UpdateUser" function shorted as result.
- Global implicit variable added for 4 variables.

### Fixed
- Circular dependency err fixed.

## [1.1.2] - 2022-12-01
-------------------------------------------------------------------
### Added
- Added new security improvements code.

### Changed
- AuthenticateConsultion and AccountConsultion is changed.

### Fixed
- Bug and NoSQL injection fixed.

## [1.1.1] - 2022-11-29
-------------------------------------------------------------------

### Added 
- Added a registration system and an entry system was introduced.

### Changed
- Code optimizations were made.
- Unnecessary modules removed.
- Global module library used.
- Encryption algorithms were improved.

## [1.1.0] - 2022-11-25
